    public final class BarTimeChart<S extends PeriodSetPlot>
extends PeriodChart<S>
    BarTimeChart This is the bar chart equivalent of a TimeChart and is functionally equivalent to PieTimeChart. It plots the sum of quantities over a period and uses the same mapping classes the intention is that you can use this to generate barcharts and timecharts interchangably. Unlike TimeCharts only a single dataset is plotted. This defaults to the last created Plot but can be reset using the #setPlot(PeriodSetPlot) method.
